  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Casa Albertina offers great value accommodation and a wonderful service in Positano.</p>
<p>This charming three-star property is set into the cliffs and is accessed by around 76 steps. Once you’ve made the climb to the hotel though, you’re rewarded with some of the most spectacular views of Positano. Panoramic terraces have been equipped with sun loungers so you can make the most of the sea views. Inside, the hotel has been decorated in a typical Neapolitan style with whitewashed walls and characteristic Mediterranean furniture. Guests rooms offer plenty of comfort with modern amenities and balconies with sea views.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 15 mins by private car from Naples Airport</p>]]></description>
